<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link923318" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=923318&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F647154-do-the-different-stories-sometimes-make%2Fanswers%2F923318-it-is-definitely-not">flag</a>
</div>
