        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer199096853" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9765545569585903697">Another absolutely lovely book by Alice Hoffman. I cannot think of a fiction writer who is better at describing the outdoors. She makes me see the sunlight filtering through the trees, leaving honey-colored splotches on the ground. I can hear the locusts, smell the lilacs and feel the moss between my toes. A year from now I won&apos;t be able to remember a thing about this book other than the fact that reading it made me feel quite pleased with the universe.</span>
  <span id="freeText9765545569585903697" style="display:none">Another absolutely lovely book by Alice Hoffman. I cannot think of a fiction writer who is better at describing the outdoors. She makes me see the sunlight filtering through the trees, leaving honey-colored splotches on the ground. I can hear the locusts, smell the lilacs and feel the moss between my toes. A year from now I won't be able to remember a thing about this book other than the fact that reading it made me feel quite pleased with the universe.</span>
