<span id="freeTextContainer7692460110857355713">I&apos;m new to this author but haven&apos;t been disappointed yet. This is a series of short stories spanning around 250 years covering the people of Blackwell. The only criticism I would have would be some stories stopped short for me. Thus being &quot;short stories&quot;. I&apos;m a detail person so I wanted to know the whys and hows of every story. Sometimes it left you hanging to gleam from it what you will. Very well written! I&apos;m a Hoffman fan as of a few weeks ago. I look forward to more of her tales. </span>
  <span id="freeText7692460110857355713" style="display:none">I'm new to this author but haven't been disappointed yet. This is a series of short stories spanning around 250 years covering the people of Blackwell. The only criticism I would have would be some stories stopped short for me. Thus being "short stories". I'm a detail person so I wanted to know the whys and hows of every story. Sometimes it left you hanging to gleam from it what you will. Very well written! I'm a Hoffman fan as of a few weeks ago. I look forward to more of her tales. </span>
