<div id="review_1371856219" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1371856219" />
    <a title="Cathie" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/12090607-cathie"><img alt="Cathie" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1483065413p2/12090607.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1371856219?book_show_action=true">Oct 01, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Cathie" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Cathie" href="/user/show/12090607-cathie">Cathie</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780307405975" href="/book/show/9852835-the-red-garden">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12090607-cathie?shelf=historical-fiction">historical-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12090607-cathie?shelf=usa-massachussetts">usa-massachussetts</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12090607-cathie?shelf=magical-realism">magical-realism</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12090607-cathie?shelf=favourite-author-books">favourite-author-books</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12090607-cathie?shelf=2016-reads">2016-reads</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12090607-cathie?shelf=community">community</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1371856219" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12470043524714739669">This book spans from 1786 to the 1990s. Each chapter is a different time in the history and community of Blackwell, Massachusetts, from it&apos;s first settlers to a story about a son returning home for his father&apos;s funeral probably sometime in the 1990s. <br/><br/>Alice Hoffman is a storyteller. She knows how to frame a story and then how to take you along so you need to know what&apos;s going to happen and how it ends. This was a wonderful journey and a reminder that we have roots even if we don&apos;t always want the</span>
  <span id="freeText12470043524714739669" style="display:none">This book spans from 1786 to the 1990s. Each chapter is a different time in the history and community of Blackwell, Massachusetts, from it's first settlers to a story about a son returning home for his father's funeral probably sometime in the 1990s. <br /><br />Alice Hoffman is a storyteller. She knows how to frame a story and then how to take you along so you need to know what's going to happen and how it ends. This was a wonderful journey and a reminder that we have roots even if we don't always want them.</span>
  <a data-text-id="12470043524714739669" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
